Questions:
If you choose to withdraw from the gratitude journaling intervention study, what will happen?
A) You will be required to pay a penalty fee for early withdrawal;
B) You will continue to be part of the study but will not have to participate in journaling;
C) Your decision to withdraw will not affect your entitlement to benefits or result in any penalties;
D) You will be obligated to complete the study once you have started.

Correct answer: C
